{
  "chapter": 13,
  "chapter_summary": "第十三回 七杀阵：风四娘与萧十一郎在面摊吃面时，七名盲人突袭，为首者是昔日点苍掌门谢天石，扇上写着\"必杀萧十一郎\"。七人摆出\"天昏地暗七杀大阵\"，以琴声驱动明杖织成压力网。萧十一郎破阵斩断明杖，杖中毒烟使风四娘昏迷。卖面跛足老人原来就是轩辕三缺，他设下此局后放过萧十一郎，却在他腿上划伤。萧十一郎带风四娘回府，发现冰冰失踪、解药被盗。轩辕三成来访，以救风四娘为名要挟萧十一郎将人交给他。萧十一郎无奈妥协，轩辕三成带走风四娘。萧十一郎独自在月下思索，决心去找他们。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_tian_shi",
      "speaker_name": "谢天石",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "你就算不出声，我也知道你在这里。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 51,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_xie_tian_shi",
      "text": "我本来就在这里。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 53,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_tian_shi",
      "speaker_name": "谢天石",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "很好，好极了。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 55,
      "line_end": 55
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_tian_shi",
      "speaker_name": "谢天石",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "你看见这六个字没有？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 65,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_xie_tian_shi",
      "text": "他当然看见了，他又不是瞎子。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 67,
      "line_end": 69
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_tian_shi",
      "speaker_name": "谢天石",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "很好，你果然也在这里。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 71,
      "line_end": 72
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_xie_tian_shi",
      "text": "是谁告诉你，我们在这里的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 75,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_xie_tian_shi",
      "text": "是花如玉？还是轩辕三成？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 79,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_xie_tian_shi",
      "text": "无论是谁告诉你们的，我都知道他是为了什么。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 83,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_tian_shi",
      "speaker_name": "谢天石",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "你知道？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 85,
      "line_end": 86
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_xie_tian_shi",
      "text": "他是想叫你们来送死。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 87,
      "line_end": 89
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_xie_tian_shi",
      "text": "但现在我却不愿看杀人，所以你们最好还是快走。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 87,
      "line_end": 89
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_xie_tian_shi",
      "text": "有很多人在杀人前，都喜欢喝杯酒的，我可以请你们喝两杯。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 107,
      "line_end": 109
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_tian_shi",
      "speaker_name": "谢天石",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "我们现在想喝的不是酒，是血，你的血！",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 111,
      "line_end": 111
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_san_que",
      "text": "是你！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 203,
      "line_end": 204
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_que",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三缺",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "你知道我是谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 205,
      "line_end": 207
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_san_que",
      "text": "轩辕三缺？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 209,
      "line_end": 210
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_que",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三缺",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "想不到你非但能破了我的天昏地暗，七杀大阵，还能认得出我来。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 211,
      "line_end": 213
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_san_que",
      "text": "若非刚才见过轩辕三成，我也想不到是你。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 215,
      "line_end": 216
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_que",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三缺",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "好个萧十一郎，果然是个聪明人，就凭这一点，我今日且放过你，快去想法子救你的女人吧，若是再迟片刻，就来不及了。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 219,
      "line_end": 221
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_que",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三缺",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "只不过老夫平生出手，例不空回，今天就算让你走，你也该留下件东西。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 225,
      "line_end": 227
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_san_que",
      "text": "大盗萧十一郎，生平只知道要人的东西，从来也没有留下过东西给别人。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 229,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_que",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三缺",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "今日你只怕就要破例一次。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 233,
      "line_end": 233
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_san_que",
      "text": "好，我就留下这一刀！",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 235,
      "line_end": 235
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_que",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三缺",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "萧十一郎，你今日还是留下了一滴血。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 251,
      "line_end": 251
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_san_que",
      "text": "这滴血是要你用血来还的。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 253,
      "line_end": 253
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_san_cheng",
      "text": "想不到你居然还敢到这里来。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 351,
      "line_end": 352
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三成",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "我不是来找你打架的，我这次来，完全是一番好意。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 355,
      "line_end": 356
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_san_cheng",
      "text": "好意？你这个人还会有好意？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 359,
      "line_end": 359
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三成",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "对别人也许不会，可是对你们两位……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 361,
      "line_end": 362
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三成",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "我实在想不到我那位六亲不认的大哥，竟会对你们下这种毒手。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 365,
      "line_end": 367
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_san_cheng",
      "text": "轩辕三缺真是你嫡亲的兄长？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 369,
      "line_end": 370
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三成",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "但我却不是他那种心狠手辣的人。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 373,
      "line_end": 373
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_san_cheng",
      "text": "你难道是想来救人的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 381,
      "line_end": 381
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_san_cheng",
      "text": "你能救得了她？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 385,
      "line_end": 385
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三成",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "我们兄弟一向很少见面，纵然见了面也很少说话，就因为我们的脾气不同，嗜好也不同。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 387,
      "line_end": 389
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_san_cheng",
      "text": "有什么不同？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 391,
      "line_end": 391
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三成",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "他喜欢杀人，我喜欢救人，只要他能杀的人，我就能救得活。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 393,
      "line_end": 394
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_san_cheng",
      "text": "你的确比他聪明，杀人对自己一点好处也没有，救人才有好处的。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 397,
      "line_end": 398
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三成",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "阁下说的这句话，实在是深得我心。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 401,
      "line_end": 401
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_san_cheng",
      "text": "这次你想要什么好处？",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 403,
      "line_end": 403
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三成",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "我什么好处也不想要，只不过……",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 405,
      "line_end": 405
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_san_cheng",
      "text": "只不过怎样？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 407,
      "line_end": 407
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三成",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "你若种了棵树，树上若是长出橘子来，橘子应该归谁？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 409,
      "line_end": 410
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_san_cheng",
      "text": "应该归我。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 413,
      "line_end": 413
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三成",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "不错，当然应该归你，因为你若不种那棵树，就根本没有橘子。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 415,
      "line_end": 416
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三成",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "现在她等于已是个死人，我若能救活了她，我就是她的重生父母，她这个人当然也该归我。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 421,
      "line_end": 423
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_san_cheng",
      "text": "放你的屁。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 425,
      "line_end": 425
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三成",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "生意不成仁义在，你就算不答应，也用不着发脾气的。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 427,
      "line_end": 429
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三成",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "在下就此告辞。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 431,
      "line_end": 431
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三成",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "阁下既然不愿我救她，我只好告辞，阁下为何要拦住我？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 437,
      "line_end": 439
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_san_cheng",
      "text": "你非救她不可。",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 441,
      "line_end": 441
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三成",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "阁下武功盖世，若是一定要逼我救她，我也不能反抗，只不过，救人和杀人也是完全不同的。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 443,
      "line_end": 445
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_san_cheng",
      "text": "有什么不同？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 447,
      "line_end": 447
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三成",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "杀人只要随随便便一出手，就可以杀一个，救人却得要花很多心血，费很多精神，若是心不甘、情不愿，就难免会疏忽大意，到了那时，阁下却怪不得我。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 449,
      "line_end": 450
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三成",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "常言说得好，死马不妨当作活马医，现在她反正已无异是个死人，阁下又何妨将她交给我？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 457,
      "line_end": 459
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_san_cheng",
      "text": "好，我就把她交给你。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 461,
      "line_end": 461
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三成",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "这本是两厢情愿的事，谁也没有勉强谁。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 463,
      "line_end": 463
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三成",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
